# Foot Terminal

## Scrollback
# Scroll up
Shift+PageUp

# Scroll down
Shift+PageDown

## Search
# Search scrollback
Ctrl+Shift+r

## Copy/Paste
# Copy selection
Ctrl+Shift+c

# Paste
Ctrl+Shift+v

## Font Size
# Increase
Ctrl++

# Decrease
Ctrl+-

# Reset
Ctrl+0

## URLs
# Open URL hint overlay
Ctrl+Shift+u
